# Overlord Item definitions
# Ver 0.1 12.11.2001

KEYWORD ITEM

ITEM coin
NAME coin
PLURAL coins
CATEGORY 1
TEXT The monetary unit

ITEM mana
NAME mana
PLURAL mana
TYPE 2
TEXT The magical power unit. Cannot be given or gotten. Its tag is [mana]

ITEM msym
NAME mystical symbol
PLURAL mystical symbols
UNIQUE
WEIGHT 1
TEXT The symbol of the arch-mage. Possession of the mystical symbol is a requirement for the most advanced spells

ITEM fate
NAME fate point
PLURAL fate points
TEXT Fate points, either in a unit's possession, or in a faction pool, may be used by any single-figure unit with the order FATE
